Buildkite sponsor

Shorthand: A CSS Framework for Designers=20
( https://shorthandcss.com/ ) =E2=80=94 Includes a =E2=80=9Clite=E2=80=9D (=
only gray) and
=E2=80=9Cfull=E2=80=9D version. This is similar to utility class-based
frameworks, so the draw here is that you don=E2=80=99t have to write any
CSS, just add classes.

Jiten Bansal

1loc: A Collection of One-line JS Snippets ( https://1loc.dev/ )  =E2=80=94=
